A quick list of direct tracking links, for when you have to construct one
manually from a tracking number.

UPS:
https://wwwapps.ups.com/tracking/tracking.cgi?tracknum=<num>

Fedex: (unconfirmed)
"http://www.fedex.com/Tracking?cntry_code=us&tracknumbers="& {!Tracking__c} ,"Track "& {!Name} &" - "&{!SerialNumber}

USPS: (unconfirmed)
"http://trkcnfrm1.smi.usps.com/PTSInternetWeb/InterLabelInquiry.do?origTrackNum="& {!Tracking__c} ,"Track "& {!Name} &" - "&{!SerialNumber}

Canada Post: (unconfirmed)

DHL: (unconfirmed)
"http://track.dhl-usa.com/TrackByNbr.asp?ShipmentNumber="& {!Tracking__c} ,"Track "& {!Name} &" - "&{!SerialNumber}

Purolator: (unconfirmed)
"https://www.purolator.com/purolator/ship-track/="& {!Tracking__c} ,"Track "& {!Name} &" - "&{!SerialNumber}
http://www.purolator.com/purolator/ship-track/tracking-details.page?pin="& Tracking_Number__c
